text: Bishindeegiin Urantungalag (born 24 February 1977) is a Mongolian archer. Urantungalag competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Bishindeegiin Urantungalag == References == Category:Living people Category:1977 births Category:Mongolian archers Category:Olympians for Mongolia
